You think it’s new, a fad, silly … but it’s not … and the behavior of humans And why the long term opportunity is real is based in the fact that we have been pondering this for over a decade. 

Been on … just been waiting for the timing ⏱ to matter to e masses …

We are in the beginning, but this is going to be a fun decade with many ups and downs but web3 is here, please spend 25 hours of learning about the space, it can help many of you get to professional happiness

node.text: I really want people to understand how much of an opportunity there is out here for people with conviction, will, gusto, appetite … because this garage sale flip life shit is game changing, I get emails daily from people who started it and are stunned where they are a year later starting with only $200 … #TrashTalk episode 6 is coming shortly but here is a preview of my best moment. After going ice 🧊 cold 🥶 for 2-3 hours and getting literally nothing in the first 20 sales .. I hit a mother load of Manga Japanese books 📚 for $270 that will go bananas 🍌 on EBay ✅… y’all can do it … please get yours
